snippet.title: Labyrinth Teaser
snippet.description:
Labyrinth is the marriage between CCG and tactical RPG, where you play both adventurer and dungeon master. Tabletop adventure feel in an immersive 3D world.  

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=527898055
Thank you very much for your support!  Labyrinth was one of the top 5 games Greenlit on October 8, 2015.
